Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:21.66,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想逃离现代生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:23.92,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}每次触碰都改变的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:29.09,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}将「那是拟人化」的诡辩揉成纸团丢掉  来跳舞吧
